Compatible with iOS 8, 9, 10, 11 and 12
arm64e/A12 not yet supported.

Bypass jailbreak detection on CIMB Clicks app.

This tweak supports the latest version of CIMB Clicks Apps VER 6.1.23 and may still be suitable for later versions.

No congfigure options.

For the first time, you need to close the apps background and launch it again for it to work.
